{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Immersive controls</h2>Jump into the real-sized driver\u2019s seat, turn up the volume, and feel the speed and the kick of adrenaline. Enjoy the VR-native controls: turn the wheel with your hands, adjust mirrors, and control the gearbox and car computer. Your car is so much more in virtual reality!<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/01-G-upd.gif?t=1726560687\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Real licensed cars</h2>Have you ever imagined what it would be like to get in the seat of the <i>Nissan GT-R 2021 Track Edition</i>? Or maybe <i>Jaguar XE SV Project 8</i>? Say no more because you will have a real car and real feelings here.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/02-G-upd.gif?t=1726560687\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Compete and hang out with real people</h2>Have fun with your friends or find new ones. Race or chill in the lobby, play mini-games, show off your car and your style, challenge racers, listen to music and celebrate car culture with the others.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/03-G-upd.gif?t=1726560687\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Customization</h2>Customize your car in different visual and technical variations, and develop your builds to achieve a unique gaming style and appearance.<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/extras/04-G-upd.gif?t=1726560687\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726560687","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/page.bg.jpg?t=1726560687","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1822540/capsule_231x87